<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>30</hymn_number>
<author>2nd tune ah - &quot;Khuksak u'n, Lalpen chuh.&quot;</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lal Isu min chawian hitiu,
 Angelte'n chawian hen; (2)
 A min pakthing bang chawi hitiu,
 Khuksak...un, khuksak (3) Lalpen chu khuksak un.

[V2]
 2. Pathien thihpihte'n khuksa un,
 Maicham apat samte'n; (2)
 Jesai phunga pieng chawisang un,
 Khuksak...un, khuksak (3) Lalpen chuh khuksak un.

[V3]
 3. Israel nam a kitel dawkte,
 Hatlo leh tawmte haw; (2)
 Lungsiet a hun hukdampa chuh,
 Khuksak...un, khuksak (3) Lalpen chu khuksak un.

[V4]
 4. Nanghaw Jentel migilote'n,
 A thawkna hengilh kiu; (2)
 A keng bul achun khun unla,
 Khuksak...un, khuksak (3) Lalpen chu khuksak un.

[V5]
 5. Leisiet a mi I bawnchau in,
 Phungguol leh namtin in; (2)
 Lalna chengcheng Amah pie'i tiu,
 Khuksak..un, khuksak (3) Lalpen chu khuksak un.

[V6]
 6. Thangvan a mithiengte haw tawh,
 A ma ah khun hitiu; (2)
 Kumsawt la chuh sakpih hitiu,
 Khuksak...un, khuksak (3) Lalpen chu khuksak un.</lyrics>
<title>ALL HAIL THE POWER!</title>
</song>